   416→## [8.2.0] (2021-09-10)
   417→
   418→### Added
   419→
   420→- `.showSuggestionAfterError()` to show suggestions after unknown command or unknown option ([#1590])
   421→- add `Option` support for values from environment variables using `.env()` ([#1587])
   423→### Changed
   424→
   425→- show error for unknown global option before subcommand (rather than just help) ([#1590])
   427→### Removed
