   903→  * also, action handler now passed array of unknown arguments
   904→* complain about unknown options when program argument supplied and action handler ([#1049])
   905→  * this changes parameters to `command:*` event to include unknown arguments
   906→* removed deprecated `customFds` option from call to `child_process.spawn` ([#1052])
   907→* rework TypeScript declarations to bring all types into imported namespace ([#1081])
