   945→## [3.0.1] (2019-08-30)
   946→
   947→### Added
   948→
   949→* .name and .usage to README ([#1010])
   950→* Table of Contents to README ([#1010])
   951→* TypeScript definition for `executableFile` in CommandOptions ([#1028])
   953→### Changed
